snippet.title: Amber Heard Fires Back At "DUMB" Johnny Depp Fans | Celebrity Craze
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Fires Back At "DUMB" Johnny Depp Fans | Celebrity Craze

Amber Heard went from being the model for women’s rights and feminism to one of the most hated people in Hollywood.

After she first made accusations against her ex-husband Johnny Depp back in 2016, Amber received support from both fans and fellow celebs.

However, over the years, Amber has lost almost all of her supporters as more and more people started doubting her version of events.

Check out the video as we break it down for you.
